query:
-- Verificar romaneios recentes e seus status
SELECT 
  sm.id as romaneioId,
  sm.manifestNumber,
  sm.status as statusRomaneio,
  sm.createdAt as criadoEm,
  sm.updatedAt as atualizadoEm,
  GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT po.status) as statusPedidos,
  COUNT(DISTINCT smi.pickingOrderId) as totalPedidos
FROM shipmentManifests sm
LEFT JOIN shipmentManifestItems smi ON sm.id = smi.manifestId
LEFT JOIN pickingOrders po ON smi.pickingOrderId = po.id
WHERE sm.createdAt >= DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 24 HOUR)
GROUP BY sm.id, sm.manifestNumber, sm.status, sm.createdAt, sm.updatedAt
ORDER BY sm.createdAt DESC;
